er/svg/a7ffe079afd996740883579f310cedf037846363" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.838ex; width:5.656ex; height:2.843ex;" alt=3D"{\textstyle 1/{\sq=
rt {n}}}"></span> (see <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Berry%E2%80=
