><i>x<sub>n</sub></i></span>|)</span> ensures that <span class=3D"texhtml">=
<i>X</i><sub>1</sub>, ..., <i>X<sub>n</sub></i></span> are of zero mean and=
 <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Uncorrelated" class=3D"mw-redirec=
t" title=3D"Uncorrelated">uncorrelated</a>;<sup class=3D"noprint Inline-Tem=
plate Template-Fact" style=3D"white-space:nowrap;">[<i><a href=3D"https://e=
n.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed" title=3D"Wikipedia:Citation=
